  "body": "Currently the mainnet value of the ETH1 Blocktime is set at 14 seconds, when in actuality it is 13 seconds. \r\nCurrent Value:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/configs/mainnet/phase0.yaml#L48\r\n\r\nCurrent ETH1 Blocktime(from etherscan) \r\nhttps://etherscan.io/chart/blocktime\r\n\r\nThe last time it was consistently 14 seconds was in 2018, whereas for the 2 years after it has been at about 13 seconds. \r\n\r\nThis variable is used in a few important places, mainly when creating the genesis state here:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/ad48c82ba712b7ae8988d20221aa6045915b55d0/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#genesis\r\n\r\nOr when determing a candidate eth1 block to vote on\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/ad48c82ba712b7ae8988d20221aa6045915b55d0/specs/phase0/validator.md#eth1block",
